      "paperId": "0fd3d9b4b0b1bc0e5c5e488cd8faf459b0122496",
      "title": "\u201cSimulacra of translation\u201d: reflections on the publication of Jurgen Habermas\u2019 Theory of Communicative Activity",
      "authors": [
